Brian Blessed https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brian_Blessed 0 Brian Blessed, (; born 9 October 1936) is an English actor, writer, presenter, and comedian. He is known for his booming voice and his roles in Z-Cars, I, Claudius, Blackadder, and Flash Gordon.
